author: Warner Todd Huston
title: Florida’s Governor Believes Miami Super Bowl May Have Prompted Coronavirus Outbreak
description: Florida Governor Ron DeSantis said on Wednesday that he thinks the Wuhan virus was likely in circulation during Super Bowl LIV in Miami on Feb 2.
content:
Florida Governor Ron DeSantis said on Wednesday that he thinks the Wuhan virus was likely in circulation during Super Bowl LIV in Miami on Feb 2.
